            <div class="div4">
                <p>
                    At Belgium Campus, we believe that student success goes beyond academics. It starts with your well-being. Balancing studies, social life, and personal challenges can be overwhelming, which is why we prioritize your mental, physical, and emotional health. Our Wellness Program is designed to support you through every step of your journey by offering tools, resources, and a safe space to talk. When you feel well, you can stay focused, motivated, and ready to reach your full potential both in and out of the classroom.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="div5">
                <h2>How It Works:</h2>
                <ol>
                    <li>Click Register in the top left corner of this page, if you have not yet registered</li>
                    <li>Enter your Belgium Campus student number</li>
                    <li>Provide your first and last name</li>
                    <li>Enter your official student email address.</li>
                    <li>Add a valid phone number so we can contact you if needed</li>
                    <li>Create a secure password for your account</li>
                    <li>Click “Register” to complete your profile</li>
                    <li>Once registered, log in using the registration details you have provided</li>
                    <li>Explore your dashboard, where you can view upcoming sessions, message your counselor, or update your details</li>
                    <li>Book a session with one of our trained counselors through the dashboard</li>
                    <li>Attend your session online or in person at the Wellness Center, depending on your preference</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
            
